0.1.name: wordpress/bookmark-export
0.1.description:
Bookmark Export helps you enter your Blog into several social bookmarking service. It automatically generates bookmark-files which you can easily import into these services. The plugin gets the title, description, date of the last modification and the date the post has been published. Bookmark Export safes you a lot of time if you want to import every single post or page of your blog into social bookmarking services (e.g. for pagerank-optimization ;)).

Feel free to contact me if something weird happens during usage.
